taddarśayati—nāsti bhāvaketyādi | tatkiṃ mantradevatayoruccheda evotpannakrama ityāha—tiṣṭhetāviti | niṣprapañcaḥ śūnyataikarasatvāt | svabhāvaḥ sahajamahāsukharūpaḥ | tadrūpeṇa mantradevau tiṣṭhataḥ |

<commentary>tadeva nirdiśati—vairocanetyādi |
sāttviko mūrtivānvajrasattvaḥ | vairocanādirūpeṇa niṣprapañcasvabhāvaṃ tattvamevocyata ityarthaḥ |</commentary>